The `ServerValue.TIMESTAMP` writes a UNIX-style timestamp, which is the number of milliseconds that have passed since the epoch. The value you gave corresponds to &quot;Wed Oct 09 2019 13:57:38 GMT-0700 (Pacific Daylight Time)&quot; after converting it to a date.

